node.text: @artisansdegeneve introducing the new series “Meet the Passion” and today met and interviewed John Demsey, Executive Group President of Estee Lauder,  he opens up about his  passion for fine art, customization and watchmaking

Gem setting at its finest with the one off @JacobAndCo Mystery Tourbillon blue camouflage 🔵💎 
This jaw dropping Pièce Unique with a 18K white gold case features eye-catching dial flawlessly set with hexagonal, overlapping blue shades sapphires.
Both the minute and the hour discs are set with a single white diamond to indicate the time of this striking piece.
Total carat weight: 35,41😱

At the center of the Mystery Tourbillon Camo are present Two Triple-Axis Tourbillons decorated with 2 rubies. 
⌚️tag price: $1,300,000.00
